I found the actual fixture mismatch: the cache key normalizer now includes JSON-RPC version `"2.0"`, while several old snapshots still store `null` as the version component. I’m duplicating those stale `null` keys to the new `"2.0"` form so the tests use fixtures instead of falling through to live RPC.
